{"tid":788254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"竊賊25秒偷龍轉鳳盜鑽戒","createTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T10:42:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3312433fbaeaf702015e23ec7fee79cf29c5f03","tid":788254,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180821/20481108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F20481108&d=87bkXItMRM2fHHB6Ip%2FugP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=48a1357e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F20481108&h=87ff8590\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180821/20481108</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月21日 <br />\n<br />\n竊賊25秒偷龍轉鳳盜鑽戒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180821/large/21la7p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180821%2Flarge%2F21la7p04.jpg&h=c00cba78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n珠寶店閉路電視拍下男子偷龍轉鳳過程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角一間珠寶店前日遭騙徒偷龍轉鳳偷走鑽戒，騙徒趁職員彎身取貨時下手，然後施施然離開，全程不足25秒。職員翌日點算時才發現失去一隻價值36萬元的鑽戒，於是報警。警方正追緝賊人歸案。<br />\n<br />\n現場為旺角彌敦道信和中心地下六福珠寶，《蘋果》獲得一段閉路電視錄影片段，可見一名身穿白色T恤、淺藍色牛仔褲的中年男子，右手拿着手機，左手則從托盤拿起鑽戒，然後要求職員在飾櫃內取出另一戒指。其間賊人趁職員彎身打開飾櫃時，藉機將鑽戒藏於手機底下，然後右手將預先準備好的假鑽戒放回托盤上，事成後隨即示意要離開。<br />\n<br />\n至昨上午11時許，珠寶店職員點算時揭發事件，於是報案，指懷疑店內一隻價值36萬元鑽戒被人以假戒指換走。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁澤岡  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n回收商爬貨櫃抗地署清場<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n七旬翁舞刀斬街坊頸"},{"pid":"4c76649ba10032222717dd433ac0412f022e2bcf","tid":788254,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"佢個頭做咩笠住個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"86a40b94b685b58c2fc4bf053044425a776cb725","tid":788254,"uid":79860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4c76649ba10032222717dd433ac0412f022e2bcf","tid":788254,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"佢個頭做咩笠住個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"你轆撚做咩生係你隻眼度？"},{"pid":"0e321240692481f6b776e31350af855402c3e838","tid":788254,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c76649ba10032222717dd433ac0412f022e2bcf","tid":788254,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"佢個頭做咩笠住個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbad5f70db6b421a3043c1a85f6a73d1ab1f976","tid":788254,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c76649ba10032222717dd433ac0412f022e2bcf","tid":788254,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"佢個頭做咩笠住個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"驚畀高空監示鏡頭影到嘛。"},{"pid":"c22279236cd568ad713ebd1824bda7e108e10f47","tid":788254,"uid":134161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e321240692481f6b776e31350af855402c3e838","tid":788254,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c76649ba10032222717dd433ac0412f022e2bcf","tid":788254,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"佢個頭做咩笠住個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"弱撚智<img